Package: nattunnel
Version: @VERSION@
Section: net
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Depends: wireguard-tools, iproute2, libx11-6, libice6, libsm6, libfontconfig1, dotnet-runtime-10.0
Maintainer: NATTunnel contributors
Homepage: https://github.com/milesthenerd/NATTunnel
Description: Mesh VPN daemon and GUI with NAT hole-punching
 NATTunnel creates WireGuard tunnels between peers behind NAT, using a
 mediation server to coordinate UDP hole-punching. Peers form a fully
 decentralized mesh where every peer can reach every other peer.
 .
 This package ships the daemon (nattunneld) managed by systemd and a
 desktop GUI (nattunnel-gui) that attaches to the running daemon.
